Subject: [PATCH 448/540] Add kernel version checking macro

It contains a macro to help checking for kernel version ranges.

Signed-off-by: Simon Marchi <simon.marchi@polymtl.ca>
Signed-off-by: Mathieu Desnoyers <mathieu.desnoyers@efficios.com>
---
 drivers/staging/lttng2/lttng-kernel-version.h | 36 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 36 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 drivers/staging/lttng2/lttng-kernel-version.h

diff --git a/drivers/staging/lttng2/lttng-kernel-version.h b/drivers/staging/lttng2/lttng-kernel-version.h
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..280a398
--- /dev/null
+++ b/drivers/staging/lttng2/lttng-kernel-version.h
@@ -0,0 +1,36 @@
+#ifndef _LTTNG_KERNEL_VERSION_H
+#define _LTTNG_KERNEL_VERSION_H
+
